text: Whoever Comes Knocking is the third studio album by Ghanaian-Canadian Singer- songwriter Kae Sun. It was released on March 2, 2018, by Moonshine. He revealed the album's track listing in December 2017. ==Track listing== # Kwaku's Dilemma (Intro) # Treehouse # Stalk # Canary # Longwalk # Fix Up (ft.
